;Mozilla Firefox Web Browser
Brabhsair-lìn Mozilla Firefox


;Websites you use with Firefox can send you notifications in the background that can appear on screen or update the web page. You can control how these notifications appear and work.
Nuair a thadhlas tu air làrach ann am Firefox, tachraidh gun cuir e brathan thugad sa chùlaibh agus gun nochd iad sin air an sgrìn no gun ùraich iad an duilleag-lìn. ’S urrainn dhut smachd a chumail air na brathan seo.


;What is Push?
Dè tha ann am Push?


;Push is an optional feature that allows websites to send you messages even when you aren’t visiting the site.
’S e gleus roghainneil a tha ann am Push a bheir cead do làraichean-lìn brathan a chur thugad fiù mur eil thu air an làrach.


;Sites can use this feature to provide you with notifications or update data in the background.
Tha an gleus seo feumail do làraichean ach an urrainn dhut fios a chumail riut no dàta ùrachadh sa chùlaibh.


;For instance, a webmail site might use Push to provide you with a notification when new messages arrive, or a weather site might use Push to provide storm alerts.
Mar eisimpleir, ’s urrainn do làrach puist-lìn Push a chleachdadh ach an urrainn dha innse dhut nuair a gheibh thu teachdaireachd ùr no làrach aimsire airson rabhadh a chur thugad mun t-sìde.


;You will only receive messages from sites for which you have granted permission.
Chan fhaigh thu brathan ach o theachdaireachdan a thug thu cead dhaibh.


;How does it work?
Ciamar a dh'obraicheas e?


;Firefox maintains a connection to a push service.
Glèidhidh Firefox ceangal ri seirbheis push.


;Sites that you have granted permission for Push can use the service to send you messages.
Ma thug thu cead do làrach, ’s urrainn dha Push brathan a chur thugad slighe na seirbheise.


;Firefox delivers this push message to a small piece of JavaScript called a “worker”.
Libhrigidh Firefox am brath push seo do phìos beag de JavaScript air a bheil “obraiche”.


;The worker then processes the message.
Dèiligidh an t-obraiche ris a’ bhrath.


;It might decide to show a visual notification or store the message for later use.
Dh’fhaoidte gun nochd e brath lèirsinneach no gun glèidh e am brath airson a chur gu feum uaireigin eile.


;What information do I share with a site?
Dè am fiosrachadh a bhios mi a’ nochdadh ri làrach?


;A site can use Push to send you a message at any time, even when you are not actively visiting it.
’S urrainn do làrach Push a chleachdadh gus brath a chur thugad aig uair sam bith, fiù mur eil thu ’ga chleachdadh.


;A site that sends you a message can learn your IP address if it chooses to do so; this could reveal your location.
Chì làrach a chuireas brath thugad an seòladh IP agad ma thogras e agus dh’fhaoidte gun aithnichear d’ ionad ri linn sin.


;What information does Firefox use to provide Push?
Dè am fiosrachadh a bheir Firefox dha Push?


;Firefox maintains a permanent connection to a push service in order to receive push messages.
Glèidhidh Firefox ceangal buan ri seirbheis push ach an urrainn dha brathan push a chur thugad.


;On our server we store a randomized identifier for your browser, along with a randomized identifier for each site you authorize.
Cumaidh sinn aithnichear air thuaiream airson a’ bhrabhsair agad air na frithealaichean againn agus aithnichear air thuaiream airson gach làrach a bheir thu cead dha.


;On Firefox for desktop, the push service is operated by Mozilla.
’S e Firefox a tha ag obrachadh na seirbheise push mu choinneamh Firefox desktop.


;Firefox for Android uses the same <a href="%s">Google Cloud Messaging</a> platform and infrastructure that your other Android applications use.
Tha Firefox airson Android a’ cleachdadh an aon ùrlar is bun-structar <a href="%s">Google Cloud Messaging</a> ’s a chleachdas an corr dhe na h-aplacaidean Android agad.


;In both cases, the push service cannot decrypt your push messages.
Air an dà ùrlar seo, chan urrainn dhan t-seirbheis push na brathan push agad a dhì-chrioptachadh.


;Push messages are encrypted, only your copy of Firefox can decipher them.
Thèid na brathan Push a chrioptachadh agus chan urrainn ach dhan Firefox agad fhèin a leughadh.


;The encrypted messages are stored on the server until they are delivered.
Thèid na brathan crioptaichte a chumail air an fhrithealaiche gus an dèid an libhrigeadh.


;How do I revoke Push permissions?
Ciamar a bheir mi air falbh ceadan a thaobh Push?


;To stop a site from sending you push messages:
Dèan na leanas airson casg a chur air brathan push o làrach:


