Fosgail na <em>Roghainnean</em>


;Click on <em>Content</em> and under Notifications, select <em>Choose…</em>
Briog air <em>Susbaint</em> agus fon earrann “Brathan”, tagh <em>Tagh…</em>


;Select the site.
Tagh an làrach.


;Select <strong>Remove Site</strong>.
Tagh <strong>Thoir air falbh an làrach</strong>.


