;How do I disable Push permanently?
Ciamar a chuireas mi Push à comas gu buan?


;Push is always opt-in in Firefox.
Cha bhi Push a’ dol o thùs ann am Firefox.


;A site cannot send you push messages without your permission.
Chan urrainn do làrach brathan push a chur thugad gun do chead iarraidh ro làimh.


;If you wish to disable the feature completely, please follow these steps:
Ma tha thu airson an gleus a chur à comas buileach, lean ris na ceuman a leanas:


;Select <strong>Remove All Sites</strong>.
Tagh <strong>Thoir air falbh gach làrach</strong>.


;Websites will not be able to send you messages and will need to ask your permission to send them in the future.
Chan urrainn do làraichean-lìn brathan a chur thugad agus feumaidh iad do chead iarraidh mus urrainn dhaibh an cur a-rithist.


