# Obsolete string, do not remove
;Set the <em>Receive Push Notifications</em> to <strong>Block</strong>. Websites will not be able to send you messages or ask for access to Push.
Tagh <strong>Bac</strong> airson <em>Faigh brathan Push</em>. Chan urrainn do làraichean brathan a chur thugad no cead airson Push iarraidh ort tuilleadh.


;What’s New?
Dè tha ùr?


;Firefox has delivered on-screen notifications to open web pages for the last several releases.
Tha Firefox air a bhith a’ libhrigeadh brathan air an sgrìn do dhuilleagan-lìn ann an grunn sgaoilidhean gu ruige seo.


;With Firefox 44, users can receive notifications associated with a web page even if they navigate away from the site or close the tab via a mechanism called Push.
A-mach o Firefox 44, is urrainn do chleachdaichean brathan fhaighinn a tha co-cheangailte ri duilleag-lìn fiù mur eil iad air an làrach tuilleadh no ma dhùineas iad an taba slighe gleus air a bheil Push.


;With Push, sites can update data in the background even without showing you a notification.
’S urrainn do làraichean dàta ùrachadh sa chùlaibh slighe Push, fiù gun a bhith a’ nochdadh brath riut.


;If you already gave permission to a site to send notifications, these sites will also be able to use this Push mechanism.
Ma thug thu cead do làrach brathan a chur thugad roimhe seo, ’s urrainn dha na làraichean seo an gleus Push seo a chleachdadh.


;If you wish to change notifications preferences, open the Content>Notifications section in Preferences/Options or click the options in one of the notifications you receive.
Ma tha thu airson roghainnean nam brathan atharrachadh, fosgail an earrann “Susbaint” > “Brathan” sna roghainnean no briog air na roghainnean ann am brath a fhuair thu.


;Will this cost me money?
An cosg seo airgead?


;Push uses a small amount of data to operate.
Cleachdaidh Push uiread beag a dhàta.


;If you’re on a small data allowance, or are charged for any data usage, you may wish to monitor your usage.
Ma tha an dàta agad cuingichte no ma phàigheas tu airson dàta a chaitheas tu, dh’fhaoidte gum b’ fheairrde dhut sùil a chumail air na chaitheas tu dheth.


;How do I add Push to my web site?
Ciamar a chuireas mi Push ris an làrach-lìn agam?


;The <a href="%s">Push API specification</a> explains how to create a Service Worker and send push messages.
Tha am <a href="%s">Push API Specification</a> a’ mìneachadh mar a chruthaichear obraiche seirbheise agus mar a chuirear brathan push.


